      "textUthmaniTajweed": "إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْإِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نس</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>نَ لِرَبِّه<tajweed class=madda_normal>ِۦ</tajweed> لَكَن<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>د</tajweed>ٌ <span class=end>٦</span>",
